"uid":43060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T15:35:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>定係香港人著衫係計月份<br />\n4-10 就短袖<br />\n11-3就羽絨 頸巾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n3-12短袖<br />\n1-4長袖<br />\n<br />\n香港已經唔會有機會著到羽絨"},{"pid":"374b212689f0475b97de4ca04b6a998d4276577b","tid":482771,"uid":3782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T15:40:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>琴日著短袖都比人眼啤啤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔凍就唔撚著咁多架啦 20度冷帽大褸都唔知做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n望下唔撚畀㗎?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有話唔望得咩 我講我見到有人係咁望喳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁係咁望又有咩問題要你喺到猜度呢?<br />\n睇你咁多抱怨就知係想投訴人望你嘅動機啦<br />\n你會唔會係有菜sip 咗喺牙罅喳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有咩好投訴 望又望左啦 又唔係有咩唔見得光:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係覺得著短袖有咩出奇要望姐<br />\n轉番轉你都可以話樓主做乜要出post話人好著咁多衫架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e0945cc2599381a84cc5649312e6a1cce236c8a","tid":482771,"uid":14244,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T15:50:36.000Z","msg":"22度 帶冷帽著羽絨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58e41b315a86d08c6f358368f5f3d30c68d1c97e","tid":482771,"uid":14965,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T15:52:52.000Z","msg":"十五度，西班牙人穿大衣、戴手套；西伯利亞人作日光浴。<br />\n十度，法國人開暖氣；西伯利亞人在花園裡種花。<br />\n五度，義大利人發不動車子，西伯利亞人開敞篷車遊街。<br />\n零下五度，加州人凍斃了；西伯利亞人在戶外烤肉。<br />\n零下十度，英國人開暖氣；西伯利亞人開始穿長袖。<br />\n零下五十度，北極熊撤離北極；西伯利亞軍隊延後冬季野外求生訓練，等待真正的冬天到來。<br />\n零下一百八十三度，食物中的微生物死亡；西伯利亞牛隻抱怨酪農的手太冰。<br />\n零下兩百七十三度，原子停止活動；西伯利亞人終於說：『老天，外面好冷！』<br />\n高登仔：『最近天氣開始轉涼了！』"},{"pid":"41486bc0c1d3e81c971432b5782f7876f96a6c7a","tid":482771,"uid":109086,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T16:01:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>琴日著短袖都比人眼啤啤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔凍就唔撚著咁多架啦 20度冷帽大褸都唔知做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n望下唔撚畀㗎?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有話唔望得咩 我講我見到有人係咁望喳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁係咁望又有咩問題要你喺到猜度呢?<br />\n睇你咁多抱怨就知係想投訴人望你嘅動機啦<br />\n你會唔會係有菜sip 咗喺牙罅喳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有咩好投訴 望又望左啦 又唔係有咩唔見得光:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係覺得著短袖有咩出奇要望姐<br />\n轉番轉你都可以話樓主做乜要出post話人好著咁多衫架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我今日都俾人望 個眼神仲要覺得你係痴線咁<br />\n老老實實咁樣比人望法係人都唔舒服啦"},{"pid":"173196dab9c1deec64ef4361d600651f39266c71","tid":482771,"uid":136252,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T16:04:58.000Z","msg":"你識乜呀，拍緊冬日戀曲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c860fb59cc00e8b9260c1c96c1eb1082a842b18","tid":482771,"uid":3604